<div class="story"><p>Southern Shores Landing is a town house style community in Southern Shores consisting of 38 units. Property 0wners take possession of the land directly under their respective unit, the footprint of the unit, and the HOA owns the land around each unit. The home owners association takes care of the landscaping for each units front, back and sides yards in addition to the exterior of each unit including the siding and roof. Southern Shores Landing is set up sort of like a condominium but in a town house setting. If you are looking for a maintenance free experience, then the community of Southern Shores Landing might be for you </p>
